help.title: Help{lang:separator}{embed:title}
help.description:
`{bot:prefix}{cmd:name} play <URL | Search Word>`, `{bot:prefix}{cmd:name} p <URL | Search Word>`:
・__Play the media at the URL if a URL is specified.__
`{bot:prefix}{cmd:name} pause`:
・__Pause playing media__
`{bot:prefix}{cmd:name} resume`:
・__Resume playback of paused media__
`{bot:prefix}{cmd:name} stop`:
・__Stop playback and delete queue contents__
`{bot:prefix}{cmd:name} skip`:
・__Skip to the next media in the queue__
`{bot:prefix}{cmd:name} volume <Number>`, `{bot:prefix}{cmd:name} vol <Number>`:
・__Set volume to specified number__ (Warning if the number is 120 or more)
`{bot:prefix}{cmd:name} queue`, `{bot:prefix}{cmd:name} q`, `{bot:prefix}{cmd:name} list`:
・__Display queue contents__
`{bot:prefix}{cmd:name} leave`, `{bot:prefix}{cmd:name} disconnect`, `{bot:prefix}{cmd:name} dis`:
・__Stop playback, delete cue content and leave voice channel__
`{bot:prefix}{cmd:name} history ...`, `{bot:prefix}{cmd:name} his ...`:
・__Display media played so far__
